Question: A dark computer screen is housed in a lighter monitor case, with controls centered on a panel at the bottom between small speakers.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://f.ptcdn.info/239/019/000/1400711300-SamsungRol-o.jpg

Right image URL: https://www.elarabygroup.com/media/catalog/product/cache/2/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/toshiba_smart_tv_40_inch_led_full_hd_40l3433dea_.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the computer screen dark?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the computer screen dark?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the monitor case lighter than the computer screen?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the monitor case lighter than the computer screen?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the controls centered on a panel at the bottom?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the controls centered on a panel at the bottom?')
ANSWER6=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there small speakers on the monitor case?')
ANSWER7=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there small speakers on the monitor case?')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4} and {ANSWER6}')
ANSWER9=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5} and {ANSWER7}')
ANSWER10=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER8} xor {ANSWER9}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER10)
```
